1. *Cijelo* vrijeme ona je plakala. (She was crying the whole time.)
2. On je *cijelo* dvorište isprepleo grmovima. (He planted shrubs all over the yard.)
3. *Cijelo* selo je bilo u strahu. (The whole village was in fear.)
4. *Cijelog* se čovjeka smijala. (She was laughing at the whole man.)
5. Ona je *cijelu* noć plakala. (She cried for the whole night.)